# Backend Rules — Omnix Runtime

Source: `packages/core/standards/backend.md`

- Validate input at the boundary (Zod / Pydantic / equivalent).
- Authenticate + authorize before business logic — never after.
- Domain errors are typed and mapped to HTTP codes at the edge.
- Never leak stack traces to clients.
- Every error log has a correlation/request ID.
- Don't block requests on slow work — enqueue.
- Config from env vars, validated at startup. Fail fast on missing required config.
- Structured logs, RED metrics, OpenTelemetry-compatible tracing.
